OL,3,CSale of disposable vapes to be banned
OL,4,Cby next summer
OL,6,FThe sale of disposable vapes will be
OL,7,Fbanned by next summer, the Government
OL,8,Fhas said.
OL,10,FNew legislation to ban the sale of
OL,11,Fsingle-use vapes from June 1, 2025 has
OL,12,Fbeen laid out in Parliament, the
OL,13,FDepartment for Environment, Food and
OL,14,FRural Affairs (Defra) confirmed on
OL,15,FWednesday.
OL,17,FIt added that businesses will have
OL,18,Funtil the deadline "to sell any
OL,19,Fremaining stock they hold and prepare
OL,20,Ffor the ban coming into force".
