OL,6,FDefra said the UK Government and
OL,7,Fdevolved governments had worked
OL,8,Fclosely on the ban and would "align
OL,9,Fcoming into force dates".
OL,11,FCircular Economy Minister Mary Creagh
OL,12,Fsaid single-use vapes were "extremely
OL,13,Fwasteful and blight our towns and
OL,14,Fcities".
OL,16,FMs Creagh added: "That is why we are
OL,17,Fbanning single use vapes as we end
OL,18,Fthis nation's throwaway culture.
