OL,6,F"This is the first step on the road to
OL,7,Fa circular economy, where we use
OL,8,Fresources for longer, reduce waste,
OL,9,Faccelerate the path to net-zero and
OL,10,Fcreate thousands of jobs across the
OL,11,Fcountry."
OL,13,FLast year, it was estimated that
OL,14,Falmost five million single-use vapes
OL,15,Fwere either littered or thrown away in
OL,16,Fgeneral waste every week in the UK `
OL,17,Falmost four times as much as the
OL,18,Fprevious year.
