OL,4,Cby next summer
OL,6,FDefra said vape usage in England had
OL,7,Fgrown by more than 400% between 2012
OL,8,Fand 2023, with 9.1% of the British
OL,9,Fpublic now buying and using the
OL,10,Fproducts.
OL,12,FHealth Minister Andrew Gwynne said:
OL,13,F"It's deeply worrying that a quarter
OL,14,Fof 11-15-year-olds used a vape last
OL,15,Fyear and we know disposables are the
OL,16,Fproduct of choice for the majority of
OL,17,Fkids vaping today.
