OL,6,F"Banning disposable vapes will not
OL,7,Fonly protect the environment, but
OL,8,Fimportantly reduce the appeal of vapes
OL,9,Fto children and keep them out of the
OL,10,Fhands of vulnerable young people.
OL,12,F"The government will also introduce
OL,13,Fthe Tobacco and Vapes Bill ` the
OL,14,Fbiggest public health intervention in
OL,15,Fa generation ` which will protect
OL,16,Fyoung people from becoming hooked on
OL,17,Fnicotine and pave the way for a smoke-
OL,18,Ffree UK."
