OL,6,FOn Monday, Health Secretary Wes
OL,7,FStreeting promised to toughen up
OL,8,Fsmoking laws with a "more ambitious"
OL,9,Fbill than the Conservatives.
OL,11,FThe Tobacco and Vapes Bill, tabled in
OL,12,Fthe last parliament, sought to prevent
OL,13,Fanyone born after January 1 2009 from
OL,14,Flegally smoking by gradually raising
OL,15,Fthe age at which tobacco can be bought.
OL,17,FIt also aimed to impose restrictions
OL,18,Fon the sale and marketing of vapes to
OL,19,Fchildren.
