OL,6,FMr Streeting told reporters at an east
OL,7,FLondon health facility on Monday: "We
OL,8,Fwill introduce the Tobacco and Vapes
OL,9,FBill before Christmas."
OL,11,FLibby Peake, head of resources at
OL,12,FGreen Alliance, said: "Disposable
OL,13,Fvapes are the last thing our children
OL,14,Fand the planet need, and for too long
OL,15,Fthe market for them has been allowed
OL,16,Fto grow unchecked."
